ice/fetch](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/blob/master/packages/fetch/README.en.md#metrics), the modified part is listed below.\n\n-   `to`: Server psm.\n-   `to_cluster`: Server cluster, can be set by `options.consul.cluster`, the result of consul service discovery may be changed after modification.\n-   `to_idc`: Server idc, can be set by `options.consul.idc`, the result of consul service discovery may be changed after modification.\n-   `mesh`: Whether use http egress mesh, the default is `0`, judge according to environment variables and `options.disableMesh`.\n    -   `0`: No, `options.disableMesh = false` or `process.env.TCE_ENABLE_HTTP_SIDECAR_EGRESS !=='True'`, at this time, the address after consul service discovery will be requested.\n    -   `1`: Yes, `options.disableMesh = true` or `process.env.TCE_ENABLE_HTTP_SIDECAR_EGRESS ==='True'`, at this time, if on faas, `process.env.SERVICE_MESH_HTTP_EGRESS_ADDR` will be requested, otherwise, `127.0.0.1:process. env.MESH_EGRESS_PORT`.\n-   `ipv6`: The consul service found whether the returned ipv6 address, the default is `0`.\n    -   `0`: No.\n    -   `1`: Yes.\n\n## Logger\n\nRelated tags are the same as [@byted-service/fetch](https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/blob/master/packages/fetch/README.en.md#logger), the modified part is listed below.\n\n<details>\n  <summary>History</summary>\n\n-   `v2.1.0`: Remove `is_fass_http_egress`.\n\n</details>\n\n-   `to`: Server psm.\n-   `to_cluster`: Server cluster, can be set by `options.consul.cluster`, the result of consul service discovery may be changed after modification.\n-   `to_idc`: Server idc, can be set by `options.consul.idc`, the result of consul service discovery may be changed after modification.\n-   `mesh`: Whether use http egress mesh, the default is `0`, judge according to environment variables and `options.disableMesh`.\n    -   `0`: No, `options.disableMesh = false` or `process.env.TCE_ENABLE_HTTP_SIDECAR_EGRESS !=='True'`, at this time, the address after consul service discovery will be requested.\n    -   `1`: Yes, `options.disableMesh = true` or `process.env.TCE_ENABLE_HTTP_SIDECAR_EGRESS ==='True'`, at this time, if on faas, `process.env.SERVICE_MESH_HTTP_EGRESS_ADDR` will be requested, otherwise, `127.0.0.1:process. env.MESH_EGRESS_PORT`.\n-   `rip`: Real request ip.\n-   `ipv6`: The consul service found whether the returned ipv6 address, the default is `0`.\n    -   `0`: No.\n    -   `1`: Yes.\n","repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service"},"files":["lib"],"engines":{"node":">=10.0.0"},"name":"@byted-service/fetch-protocol-consul","_npmVersion":"lerna/undefined/node@v14.20.0+x64 (linux)"},"1.2.3":{"_npmUser":{"email":"xieda@bytedance.com","name":"xieda"},"_npmVersion":"6.14.5","license":"ISC","main":"lib/index.js","dependencies":{"tslib":"^1.9.3","@byted-service/consul":"^2.0.0","@byted-service/fetch-core":"^1.4.3","@byted-service/helper":"^1.6.2","@byted-service/mesh":"^1.4.1","@byted/node-fetch":"^2.6.3"},"keywords":["fetch","consul"],"name":"@byted-service/fetch-protocol-consul","repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://code.byted.org/nodejs/byted-service/packages/fetch-protocol-consul"},"_id":"@byted-service/fetch-protocol-consul@1.2.3","description":"consul protocol for @byted-service/fetch","readmeFilename":"README.en.md","types":"lib/index.d.ts","_nodeVersion":"14.17.0","devDependencies":{"@types/lodash.pick":"^4.4.6","lodash.pick":"^4.4.0"},"dist":{"integrity":"sha512-wrSmpUFBgRmJAkh9XB2nQMp4+8RB9+YpJw0tG//d2F6AcSBzZFEceBhx1Uwsn/h/Ybi15Guf6Wc18Kb9GOoHHw==","shasum":"17cdad6941dbe9d72724b5dd35b4c6ce78f227a9","tarball":"https://bnpm.byted.org/@byted-service/fetch-protocol-consul/-/fetch-protocol-consul-1.2.3.tgz"},"files":["lib"],"maintainers":[{"avatar":"https://s3-fs.pstatp.com/static-resource/v1/bf5207f4-07f4-4c43-9004-b01af1aff365~?image_size=72x72&cut_type=&quality=&format=png&sticker_format=.webp","email":"liyubei@bytedance.com","name":"li